to do things like this.

00:02:42.280 --> 00:02:43.280
It's okay, Prae.

00:02:44.160 --> 00:02:45.240
Hang in there a little longer.

00:02:46.160 --> 00:02:48.280
Once I have the money
to settle everything,

00:02:48.880 --> 00:02:52.040
