thanks to Sexy May and her team.

00:25:58.400 --> 00:26:01.040
She’s here, so please give her
a round of applause.

00:26:03.520 --> 00:26:04.520
Thank you.

00:26:06.120 --> 00:26:08.960
I have something for you.

00:26:10.320 --> 00:26:11.320
